      <p class="spirit-subhead">A mobile-first flexbox grid in 12 columns, loosely based on [Bootstrap 4](https://getbootstrap.com/docs/4.0/layout/grid/). Usually found within an outer [container](/components/container.html) that determines the grid’s maximum width.</p>
