{% filter markdown %}
  ## Advanced Layout Options
  ### Offset Columns
  Push a cell to the left with an offset, leaving a blank space. Offsets follow the same measurements as columns, using the same [responsive helper classes](#responsive-column-layouts).
{% endfilter %}

{% set example %}
  <div class="spirit-container">
    <div class="spirit-container__inner">
      <div class="spirit-row">
